    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ催更群：902926115 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/946542b63a1c89b98b11549f9374310c.avif?t=1770821735\" width=780 height=220 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入一个融合水墨意境与油画质感的春秋幻想世界。雾气缭绕的山岭、废弃的竹林古道、荒芜的古代遗迹……五大风格迥异的区域等待探索。与怪物、盗匪，还有因执念化为妖魔的堕落之人战斗，搜集神秘竹简，拼凑出祸乱背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/cc69ff81d346df2ee2e6538a932157c1.poster.avif?t=1770821735\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/cc69ff81d346df2ee2e6538a932157c1.webm?t=1770821735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/cc69ff81d346df2ee2e6538a932157c1.mp4?t=1770821735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/51d4842565034c1d7ee36cff7ddd0a3e.avif?t=1770821735\" width=780 height=220 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建你的探索小队，从剑客、医师、巫祝、擂鼓勇士等12种职业中自由搭配。利用地形、角色的特性与技能来制定战术，对抗60+种类形态各异的敌人，和10+具有独特机制的Boss头目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/f3d3386f68b31ab0af5131a4ac482a3c.poster.avif?t=1770821735\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/f3d3386f68b31ab0af5131a4ac482a3c.webm?t=1770821735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/f3d3386f68b31ab0af5131a4ac482a3c.mp4?t=1770821735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗不仅考验策略，也折磨心智。侠客们可能在绝境中越战越勇，也可能因为恐惧而精神崩溃逃离。当同伴失散在险境中，你是否敢冒着全队覆灭的风险去将他寻回？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/b32027b2298dffddec9dd75df71ca30b.poster.avif?t=1770821735\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/b32027b2298dffddec9dd75df71ca30b.webm?t=1770821735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/b32027b2298dffddec9dd75df71ca30b.mp4?t=1770821735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/3fcda3061e22a4bfc16002a835e4f03c.avif?t=1770821735\" width=780 height=220 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探险归来，你可以在城镇中修整、发展、招贤纳士。兴建不同类型的建筑，招募春秋时代的传奇名士相助：信陵君魏无忌助你广纳豪杰，神匠干将为你锤炼兵器，谋圣鬼谷子则能提振全队士气。还可通过祭祀与研究不断提升队伍实力，强化装备，为下次出征做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201830/extras/7150445db40b9b840f8bff0f87a42a6b.avif?t=1770821735\" width=1284 height=548 /></span></p>",
